  <Docs>
    <summary>Implemented by any UI controls that wish to receive generic pointer events.</summary>
    <remarks>Pointers are abstract and take a different form on different platforms. On mobile, a pointer refers to a single tracked touch. On a desktop, the pointer is simply the mouse cursor. Most UI interfaces involve a single pointer.</remarks>
